            <h3 id="specs-directory" class="doc-h3">The complete specs/ directory</h3>
            <p class="doc-section-subtitle">Each file in <code style="font-family:monospace; font-size:13px;">specs/</code> is a self-contained markdown document that an LLM can consume as context. Files follow a strict, consistent template so LLMs parse them predictably.</p>

            <table class="size-table">
              <thead>
                <tr>
                  <th>File</th>
                  <th>Component</th>
                  <th>Key sections</th>
                </tr>
              </thead>
              <tbody>
                <tr>
                  <td><code>tooltip.md</code></td>
                  <td>Tooltip</td>
                  <td>Themes (dark/light/red), 9 arrow positions, RTL, token map</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td><code>button.md</code></td>
                  <td>Button</td>
                  <td>Variants, sizes, loading state, icon-only, disabled</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td><code>input.md</code></td>
                  <td>Input</td>
                  <td>States (default/focus/error/disabled), label pairing, helper text</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td><code>modal.md</code></td>
                  <td>Modal</td>
                  <td>Sizes, focus trap, overlay, dismiss behavior</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td><code>badge.md</code></td>
                  <td>Badge</td>
                  <td>Semantic colors, dot-only variant, max-count truncation</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td><code>avatar.md</code></td>
                  <td>Avatar</td>
                  <td>Sizes, image fallback, initials generation, group stacking</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
